: rgb(51,51,51)\">产品</font></a>，并且这产品全线通过80Plus Gold金牌认证，采用全模组化设计，能够充分满足发烧友的更多需求。此次我们就来为大家解析这款电源究竟如何。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><br style=\"line-height: 0; font-size: 0px\" />\r\n<img alt=\"金牌认证 简评海韵X-1250(SS-1250XM)电源\" src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/49451106/T2AXxGXsVXXXXXXXXX_!!49451106.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; cursor: pointer; border-right: black 1px solid\" /><br />\r\n<strong>海韵 X-1250(SS-1250XM) 电源 全家福</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"金牌认证 简评海韵X-1250(SS-1250XM)电源\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/49451106/T2qL4AXEVaXXXXXXXX_!!49451106.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid\" /></a><br />\r\n<strong>海韵 X-1250(SS-1250XM) 电源</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">其中标准功率和无风扇设计电源体积为160x150x86mm，而1000W和1200W大功率产品也仅仅是稍长，为160x150x86mm。无风扇产品并没有采用以往夸张的散热片，而是采用大量的镂空设计。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"金牌认证 简评海韵X-1250(SS-1250XM)电源\" src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/49451106/T2uY8BXzxaXXXXXXXX_!!49451106.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid\" /></a><br />\r\n<b>全六角形散热孔</b><