      </tr>\r\n        <tr bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-top: 5px\">\r\n            <td style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 80px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span>+5V输出电流</span></td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">24A</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-top: 5px\">\r\n            <td style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 80px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span>其它参数</span></td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">毛重：2.8kg<br />\r\n            净重：2.1kg</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-top: 5px\">\r\n            <td style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 80px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span>产品特点</span></td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">1年包换 2年维修</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">在DIY市场，海韵始终专注于高端<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">产品</font></a>的研发制造，其推出一系列<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">机箱</font></a>都受到了高端攒机用户的欢迎。今天给大家带来的是一款<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">海韵电源</font></a>，型号为<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">S12II-520铜牌</font></a>，这款<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">电源</font></a>做工精良，质量可靠，性能出众，支持最新主机板，性价比很高。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><br style=\"line-height: 0; font-size: 0px\" />\r\n<img alt=\"海韵S12II-520电源\" src=\"http://2e.zol-img.com.cn/product/51_500x2000/874/ceRE2MBljCclg.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; cursor: pointer; border-right: black 1px solid\" /><br />\r\n海韵S12II-520<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">电源</font></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">新版海韵 S12II电源全面通过80Plus铜牌认证，节能效果突出，品质更为可靠。S12II系列电源在与12V输出相关的电容，全部采用高传导铝质固态电容。利用固态电容低阻抗、高耐热及高稳定的特性，增强电源的稳定度及耐久性。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"海韵S12II-520电源\" src=\"http://2b.zol-img.com.cn/product/51_500x2000/877/cebEcucm3jytI.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid\" /></a><br />\r\n海韵S12II-520电源</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">海韵S12II-520电源出风口采用了蜂窝状设计，密集的网孔散热能力更强。在电源插口旁边设计有独立的开关键，玩家使用起来很是方便。</p>\r\n<div><span>产品：<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><font color=\"#484848\">S12II-520铜牌</font></a><a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><font color=\"#484848\">海韵</font></a><a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><font color=\"#484848\">电源</font></a><a target=\"_self\" style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\" name=\"p2651344\"><font color=\"#484848\"><img alt=\"回到顶部阅读\" align=\"absMiddle\" src=\"http://icon.zol.com.cn/doc/2010/top.png\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px\" /></font></a></span>\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 0px\">电源线材及风扇</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">产品</font></a>额定功率为520W，具备双路12V输出，而且其电流均为17A，能很好地支持多核平台的<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">处理器</font></a>和高性能<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">显卡</font></a>的稳定运行。另外这款<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">电源</font></a>的+3.3V和+5V输出的电流达到了24A，可以满足<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">主板</font></a>上的高速<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">内存</font></a>和大容量<a style=\"color: rgb(51,102,204); text-decoration: none\"><font style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51)\">硬盘</font></a>的需求。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><br style=\"line-height: 0; font-size: 0px\" />\r\n<img alt=\"海韵S12II-520电源\" src=\"http://2f.zol-img.com.cn/product/51_500x2000/881/ceQEQBKxp5Ek.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: bla