, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">●主动式PFC节能设计，转换效率达到85%+，更省电、待机功率更低</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">●三防、防潮、防尘、防虫设计，能应对各种复杂环境</div>\r\n<div style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr style=\"margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; height: 2px; color: gray; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\" />\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><strong><a style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 204);\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"back to top\" src=\"http://www.fsplifestyle.com/images/top2.png\" width=\"21\" height=\"20\" style=\"border: 0px;\" /></a></strong></div>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0.83em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\"><a name=\"Specification\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 204);\"></a>产品规格</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">\r\n    <caption style=\"margin-bottom: 0.5em; white-space: nowrap;\">Product Specification</caption>\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"background-color: rgb(230, 236, 242);\">\r\n            <td width=\"45%\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">型号</td>\r\n     