nt-size: 14px; text-decoration: none\">DIGI+ VRM数字供电控制</a></li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px; float: left; margin-left: 20px\"><a __lid=\"116\" style=\"color: #9e9e9e; font-size: 14px; text-decoration: none\">内存过流保护</a></li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px; float: left; margin-left: 20px\"><a __lid=\"117\" style=\"color: #9e9e9e; font-size: 14px; text-decoration: none\">ESD 静电防护</a></li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px; float: left; margin-left: 20px\"><a __lid=\"118\" style=\"color: #9e9e9e; font-size: 14px; text-decoration: none\">2.5倍使用寿命长效固态电容</a></li>\r\n    <li style=\"line-height: 20px; float: left; margin-left: 20px\"><a __lid=\"119\" style=\"color: #9e9e9e; font-size: 14px; text-decoration: none\">不锈钢防潮 I/O端口</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rich-content\" style=\"width: 960px; height: 550px\">\r\n<div class=\"rich_mask\" style=\"width: 960px; height: 550px; overflow: hidden\">\r\n<div class=\"rich-zone clearfix\" style=\"list-style-type: none; margin: 0px; width: 5960px\">\r\n<div class=\"unit_cut\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 960px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"background-image: none; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 10px; font-family: 微软雅黑   arial unicode ms   arial   helvetica   sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0px; height: auto; color: #353535; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; text-rendering: optimizelegibility\">华硕5重防护</h2>\r\n<h3 style=\"background-image: none; line-height: 1; margin-top: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑   arial unicode ms   arial   helvetica   sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0.4em; height: auto; color: #000000; font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; text-rendering: optimizelegibility\">全方位保护主板,主机更安全,使用更可靠</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 4em\">华硕主板藉由独家5重防护来保护您的电脑：DIGI+ VRM数字供电控制提供精准的APU供电控制；ESD静电防护，延长料件使用寿命，让华硕主板远离静电干扰和损害；板载可复式保险丝（自恢复保险丝）防止内存因过电流和短路损坏；防潮不锈钢I/O 接口，保护接口不受腐蚀侵害。华硕提供的这一系列的防护技术为主机提供了超强的安全可靠性和延长了耐用度。</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"center\" alt=\"alt\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/CN/products/Y4c8h5gYt9uQazAG/5X.jpg\" _ks_lazy_height=\"90\" _ks_lazy_width=\"90\" style=\"border-bottom-style: none; border-right-style: none; display: block; max-width: none; border-top-style: none; height: auto; margin-left: auto; vertical-align: middle; border-left-style: none; margin-right: auto\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"unit_cut\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 960px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"background-image: none; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 10px; font-family: 微软雅黑   arial unicode ms   arial   helvetica   sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0px; height: auto; color: #353535; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; text-rendering: optimizelegibility\">DIGI+数字供电控制</h2>\r\n<h3 style=\"background-image: none; line-height: 1; margin-top: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑   arial unicode ms   arial   helvetica   sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0.4em; height: auto; color: #000000; font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; text-rendering: optimizelegibility\">精准的数字供电控制,系统长效稳定</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 4em\">VRM (电压调校模块)是主板设计中最重要的部件之一。良好的VRM可智能的根据APU 实际所需功耗来提供精确的供电。华硕领先的数字供电设计采用超快的感应和响应速度，高效地提供精准的APU供电。精确的供电更可减少功耗浪费，保障供电持续，让系统获得更高的效率转换率与增强稳定性。&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span class=\"notice\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; color: #666666; font-size: 11px; padding-top: 0px\">*DIGI+ VRM功能也适用于FM2+ &amp; FM2 CPU.</span></p>\r\n<p><img class=\"center\" alt=\"alt\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/zDRJFj2HfjDphY4C/digi_2.jpg\" _ks_lazy_height=\"90\" _ks_lazy_width=\"90\" style=\"border-bottom-style: none; border-right-style: none; display: block; max-width: none; border-top-style: none; height: auto; margin-left: auto; vertical-align: middle; border-left-style: none; margin-right: auto\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"unit_cut\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 960px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"background-image: none; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 10px; font-family: 微软雅黑   arial unicode ms   arial   helvetica   sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0px; height: auto; color: #353535; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; text-rendering: optimizelegibility\">内存过流保护</h2>\r\n<h3 style=\"background-image: none; line-height: 1; margin-top: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑   arial unicode ms   arial   helvetica   sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0.4em; height: auto; color: #000000; font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; text-rendering: optimizelegibility\">预防短路造成的主板和内存损毁</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 4em\">板载可复式保险丝可有效防止过载或短路情况,在I/O端口到DRAM之间增强电子线路保护,保障系统和设备的安全使用，延长设备寿命。</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"center\" alt=\"alt\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/zDRJFj2HfjDphY4C/DRAM_2.jpg\" _ks_lazy_height=\"90\" _ks_lazy_width=\"90\" style=\"border-bottom-style: none; border-right-style: none; display: block; max-width: none; border-top-style: none; height: auto; margin-left: auto; vertical-align: middle; border-left-style: none; margin-right: auto\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"unit_cut\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 960px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"background-image: none; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 10px; font-family: 微软雅黑   arial unicode ms   arial   helvetica   sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0px; height: auto; color: #353535; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; text-rendering: optimizelegibility\">ESD静电防护</h2>\r\n<h3 style=\"background-image: none; line-height: 1; margin-top: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑   arial unicode ms   arial   helvetica   sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0.4em; height: auto; color: #000000; font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; text-rendering: optimizelegibility\">保护电脑远离静电烦恼</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 4em\">静电放电 (ESD)通常瞬间发生,造成严重电子线路损害。华硕主板独家的静电防护电路设计，静电能量通过接地线路被安全转移释放，避免元器件受到瞬间损伤。极大降低静电对主机带来的损伤几率。.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"center\" alt=\"alt\" src=\"http://www.asus.com.cn/websites/global/products/zDRJFj2HfjDphY4C/ESD_2.jpg\" _ks_lazy_height=\"90\" _ks_lazy_width=\"90\" style=\"border-bottom-style: none; border-right-style: none; display: block; max-width: none; bor